To compile: 
    $ make

You will need the SDL library to compile this program
Instructions on how to get SDL can be found here: http://lazyfoo.net/SDL_tutorials/lesson01/index.php

Accepted command flags:
    -text       Run the game in a 'wonderfully aesthetically pleasing' text-only mode

Controls:
    Graphical version:
        Left/Right          Move piece left and right
        Spacebar            Drop piece

    Text version:
        l/r                 Move piece left and right
        d                   Drop piece
